00:09:07.082 --> 00:09:07.953
un

00:09:07.953 --> 00:09:10.743
zi shraybt mir, un zi vintsht mir ikh zol gezunt zayn

00:09:10.743 --> 00:09:12.493
un ikh zol mikh vendn vayter

00:09:12.493 --> 00:09:15.188
mit di karte zol ikh vendn vos ikh broykh

00:09:15.188 --> 00:09:16.868
vayl ikh bin der ershter

00:09:16.868 --> 00:09:18.188
UND zi vil mir helfn.

00:09:18.188 --> 00:09:19.268
zi vet mir helfn.

00:09:19.268 --> 00:09:20.019
shoyn.

00:09:20.734 --> 00:09:23.194
mit eyn molt UNK m'hot nisht gehat keyn kleyder.

00:09:23.194 --> 00:09:25.494
in Shvedn iz nisht gevezn azoy vi zenen yetst

00:09:25.494 --> 00:09:30.764
az me kumt tsu forn haynt, get men a UNK ⟨voynung⟩, me get esn, me get tsu trinken, un me get s- k- shule, un me get ales.

00:09:30.764 --> 00:09:32.794
mir hobn gornisht gekrign.

00:09:32.794 --> 00:09:36.584
kh'hob nor gehat a por hoyzn mit a hemd mit a koshulke. m'iz gekumen krankerheyt dort.

00:09:36.584 --> 00:09:38.615
dort hot men gekrign alte kostyumen.

00:09:39.162 --> 00:09:40.455
gekrign alte kostyumen

00:09:40.798 --> 00:09:42.729
a por hoyzn vos past nisht far mir

00:09:42.729 --> 00:09:45.769
a por hoyzn. volt getun, zog ikh UNK dort iz geven shnayders

00:09:45.769 --> 00:09:47.604
hob nisht gevolt, zog ikh "veyst vos? ikh vel makhn."

00:09:47.604 --> 00:09:51.643
hob ikh genumen, hob ikh gekrign fun dem finef zlotes, un UNK gekrign finef UNK

00:09:52.138 --> 00:09:53.645
azoy iz dos gevezn.

00:09:53.645 --> 00:09:55.591
un mit eyn mol, farshteystu

00:09:55.615 --> 00:09:58.207
alts nokh far di WEIHNA- fa- far NOWY ROK

00:09:58.399 --> 00:09:59.675
kumt tsu forn

00:09:59.935 --> 00:10:01.211
an ambasador.

00:10:01.302 --> 00:10:03.928
s'heyst an ambasador fun di englishe armey.

00:10:04.356 --> 00:10:06.630
kumt tsu forn. ver heyst der ambasador?

00:10:06.630 --> 00:10:08.132
fun di poylishe regirung

00:10:08.132 --> 00:10:09.226
⟨KARMIOL⟩

00:10:09.739 --> 00:10:11.109
kumt tsu forn

00:10:11.109 --> 00:10:14.289
un heybt un tsu diktirn, un gebt undz, yeder eyner get undz finef

00:10:14.289 --> 00:10:15.249
KRONEN

00:10:15.249 --> 00:10:17.659
un er heybt on UNK mit undz tsu diskutirn

00:10:17.659 --> 00:10:18.809
kegn di poylishe

00:10:18.809 --> 00:10:20.434
regirung, az me zol nisht zayn mit di

00:10:20.434 --> 00:10:23.739
der ⟨ZAWACKI⟩ iz geven a reyent far di krig oykhet

00:10:24.589 --> 00:10:27.184
UND der tsveyter iz oykh gevezn. UNK s'iz geven ⟨dergegn⟩

00:10:27.184 --> 00:10:32.666
⟨zenen⟩ mir geven ⟨dergegn⟩. er hot undz getseylt. er hot undz gegebn, hot men gekrign a f- vider a por ⟨mark⟩.

00:10:32.892 --> 00:10:34.826
mit eyn mol farshteystu

00:10:35.389 --> 00:10:37.104
kumt tsu geyn a dokter

00:10:37.296 --> 00:10:38.741
a yidisher dokter

00:10:39.996 --> 00:10:42.268
er kumt tsu geyn unterzukhn alts tsunezamen

00:10:43.253 --> 00:10:46.701
zogt er tsu mir "yo, ahin aher, vi heystu?" zog ikh KOPELMAN.

00:10:46.701 --> 00:10:49.741
"oy" zogt er, "ikh hob" zogt er, EINE GUTEN khaver

00:10:49.741 --> 00:10:52.751
vos er, er iz, er iz shoyn in MALMO. er iz gekumen do aher

00:10:52.751 --> 00:10:55.425
vos er zogt a KOPELMAN hot im geratevet.

00:10:55.425 --> 00:10:57.523
"vi heyst der man?" "Tiger."

00:10:57.698 --> 00:11:01.478
dem man vos ikh hob getrofn in BERGEN BELSEN ven ikh bin geven a SANITATOR

00:11:01.478 --> 00:11:04.858
hob ikh im gegebn arayngeshlept in, in, do nokh di krig UNK shpritsn

00:11:04.858 --> 00:11:06.368
der iz shoyn in MALMO.

00:11:06.368 --> 00:11:10.560
der, un er zogt er hot gekrign a postn bar a yid, UNK men arayngekhapt, UNK gegebn a postn

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:12.310
azoy hob ikh gezogt "ikh ⟨vil⟩ nokh kumen tsu dem."

00:11:12.310 --> 00:11:13.955
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu

00:11:13.955 --> 00:11:16.105
hob ikh gevolt fo- forn keyn

00:11:16.105 --> 00:11:18.566
UNK me tor nisht aroysforn. UNK lager

00:11:18.994 --> 00:11:22.194
ikh hob mikh oyfgehoybn. ikh bin antlofn tsu fus fertsik kilometer.

00:11:22.723 --> 00:11:26.633
ikh hob shoyn gehat a por KRONEN. ikh hob gekrign dos do un gelofn tsum tsug

00:11:26.633 --> 00:11:28.163
un geforn keyn MALMO

00:11:28.163 --> 00:11:30.013
bin gekumen keyn MALMO, hob ikh getrofn

00:11:30.013 --> 00:11:32.473
dem Tiger. er iz geven bar a yid a faynem

00:11:32.473 --> 00:11:34.911
vos er iz geven a kemfer kegn di DEUTSCHEN

00:11:34.911 --> 00:11:38.381
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu, ikh bin geganen. ikh hob mikh gemoldn tsum amt

00:11:38.381 --> 00:11:39.754
vos ikh bin

00:11:39.754 --> 00:11:41.944
hot men mir gegebn spetsyel bald SOFORT

00:11:41.944 --> 00:11:44.204
UNK a fabrik vos ⟨s'hot⟩ fir toyznt mentshn

00:11:44.204 --> 00:11:46.932
alts elektriker bay HOCHSPANNUNG

00:11:46.939 --> 00:11:49.661
hob gekrign a papir. ikh bin dort gevezn

00:11:49.661 --> 00:11:51.033
umgefer tsvey vokhn

00:11:51.090 --> 00:11:52.538
un "for tsurik."

00:11:52.538 --> 00:11:55.228
ikh kum tsu forn dort in dem lager tsurik, hobn zey gemeynt

00:11:55.228 --> 00:11:57.148
me ⟨gleybt⟩ shoyn nisht. bin avekgekumen

00:11:57.148 --> 00:11:58.938
zog ikh "ikh bin gevezn do.

00:11:58.938 --> 00:12:00.768
ikh hob gekrign an arbet, un ikh vil geyn."

00:12:00.768 --> 00:12:03.441
zogt er "⟨du kenst⟩" do iz a UNK lager

00:12:03.441 --> 00:12:05.041
UNK fun danet ⟨geyst mer⟩ nisht aroys."

00:12:05.041 --> 00:12:07.601
ahin aher, zog ikh "ikh vel antloyfn."

00:12:07.601 --> 00:12:13.015
hot mikh nisht gevolt lozt- loyfn, hot mir gegebn, zogt er "ikh vel dikh shikn in a tsveytn lager arayn." hot er mikh geshikt in UNK.

00:12:13.015 --> 00:12:14.435
bin gekumen nokh UNK

00:12:14.435 --> 00:12:16.271
hobn zey gezogt ikh ken nisht, ikh vel dir shikn nokh

00:12:16.271 --> 00:12:19.851
no- RAT- BRAT- RATTVIK. bin ikh in RATTVIK gekumen, geven purim

00:12:19.851 --> 00:12:21.411
un dort getrofn yidn

00:12:21.411 --> 00:12:23.431
froyen, mener vos zey arbetn in vald

00:12:23.431 --> 00:12:26.421
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu, hob ikh gezogt "ikh blayb nisht do."

00:12:26.421 --> 00:12:28.146
bin ikh arayngeganen tsu dem lager

00:12:28.146 --> 00:12:29.866
un gezogt "her oys. ikh bin antlofn

00:12:29.866 --> 00:12:30.866
ikh ⟨vil⟩ nisht zayn do

00:12:30.866 --> 00:12:33.660
vest mir nisht gebn keyn erloybn- do hob ikh a papir, ikh krig an arbet

00:12:33.683 --> 00:12:36.287
iz er ganen, hot zey geklungen, hot er gezogt "s'iz vor.

00:12:36.287 --> 00:12:37.119
for."

00:12:37.530 --> 00:12:40.426
bin aroysgeganen fun ⟨dem⟩, iz geshtanen tsvey froyen.

00:12:40.720 --> 00:12:41.855
eyne heyst

00:12:43.268 --> 00:12:45.877
Helfer, un di tsveyte heys ⟨SHUS⟩.

00:12:45.934 --> 00:12:47.884
zey zogn zey hobn bakante

00:12:47.884 --> 00:12:50.274
khaveyrim, ir, a n- khosn

00:12:50.274 --> 00:12:52.692
in, in MALMO, un zey viln forn

00:12:52.692 --> 00:12:55.774
hot zi shoyn nisht gekent zogn neyn, zenen di froyen oykh geforn tsu mir

00:12:55.774 --> 00:12:56.994
azoy bin ikh gekumen

00:12:56.994 --> 00:12:59.494
keyn MALMO, un ikh hob gekrign a postn

00:12:59.856 --> 00:13:02.566
a g- zeyer a shtarkn, gutn postn in UNK

00:13:02.566 --> 00:13:06.156
zey hobn fardint finef KRON a vokh. ikh hob gearbet tsvey shift, fardinen

00:13:06.156 --> 00:13:07.646
hundert un akhtsik KRON.

00:13:07.646 --> 00:13:10.137
un dort ⟨hob ikh⟩ gehat a glik. umedum hob ikh glik.

00:13:10.137 --> 00:13:11.987
dort iz gevezn di shvester

00:13:11.987 --> 00:13:14.527
vos zi hot UNK MEINE froy

00:13:14.527 --> 00:13:16.553
di fabrik hot gekert tsu SCHMIDT

00:13:16.553 --> 00:13:18.153
un dos iz ⟨dos⟩ zayn shvester

00:13:18.153 --> 00:13:21.343
zi iz gevezn in roytn kreyts, d- zi mit di shvester geshtorbn

00:13:21.343 --> 00:13:23.028
hot zi genumen di hant bay mir.

00:13:23.028 --> 00:13:24.780
iz zi gevezn in UNK

00:13:24.780 --> 00:13:27.438
UNK ikh hob fardint, un ikh hob gezogt az ikh gey mit ir

00:13:27.438 --> 00:13:32.655
hot zi mir tsugenumen dos gelt yede vokh hundert un akhtsik KRON, hot mir gegebn tsvontsik KRON. kh'hob gehat esn biz do aher.

00:13:32.863 --> 00:13:35.135
un azoy hob ikh khasene gehat mit MEINE froy.

00:13:36.395 --> 00:13:38.915
yetst UNK ⟨kh'hob⟩ fun di froy vayter tsu dertseyln.

00:13:40.677 --> 00:13:41.652
yetst

00:13:41.652 --> 00:13:44.417
khasene gehat hot ir in akht un fertsikstn?

00:13:43.832 --> 00:13:45.311
akht un fertsikstn.

00:13:45.435 --> 00:13:48.331
vayter hot ir zikh antviklt mit der arbet?

00:13:47.190 --> 00:13:50.452
oh, ikh hob gehat mer mazl vi farshtand.

00:13:50.452 --> 00:13:53.962
bin ikh geforn tsum zeks, in z- in zeks un fertsikstn yor

00:13:53.962 --> 00:13:56.432
bin ikh geforn oyf di sprave tsu BIEBOWn.

00:13:56.432 --> 00:13:57.942
ikh bin der hoypt eydes

00:13:57.942 --> 00:13:59.162
bay BIEBOWn

00:13:59.162 --> 00:14:00.342
vi ikh hob gezen

00:14:00.342 --> 00:14:01.660
vi er hot geshosn

00:14:01.660 --> 00:14:04.260
m'hot gesho- d- mit dem kind fun ZIGEUNER lager

00:14:04.260 --> 00:14:06.110
un dokter Miler's tokhter.

00:14:06.110 --> 00:14:08.290
ikh hob gezen dem DAWID vi er hot geshosn

00:14:08.290 --> 00:14:09.380
un ikh hob gezen vi der

00:14:09.380 --> 00:14:11.720
er hot geharget andere, andere mentshn.

00:14:11.720 --> 00:14:12.980
dos hob ikh dertseylt

00:14:12.980 --> 00:14:14.990
UNK geven a mayse, dos. dos iz geven

00:14:14.990 --> 00:14:17.710
nayntsn zeks un fertsik, bin ikh geven in Poyln

00:14:15.979 --> 00:14:17.120
in Poyln?

00:14:17.447 --> 00:14:18.791
m'hot im oyfgehengen?

00:14:17.710 --> 00:14:18.640
oyf di sprave

00:14:18.640 --> 00:14:20.530
m'hot im oyfgehongen. m'iz geganen ale

00:14:20.530 --> 00:14:22.450
in z- GEFANGNIS arayn

00:14:22.450 --> 00:14:25.719
dort vu m'hot im gehongen. m- mir zenen geven derbay.

00:14:25.719 --> 00:14:26.909
dos iz geven nayntsn

00:14:26.909 --> 00:14:29.169
zeks un fertsik. demolt bin ikh geganen mit di froy.

00:14:29.169 --> 00:14:31.752
nayntsn hundert zibn un, zibn un fertsik

00:14:31.752 --> 00:14:33.962
bin ikh geforn vayter keyn Poyln

00:14:33.962 --> 00:14:35.422
bin ikh gevezn in Poyln

00:14:35.422 --> 00:14:39.170
un ikh hob genumen nokh, iz geven a f- sakh shteln vos UNK bahaltn

00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:41.270
vos s'iz nisht, oyfn boydem nisht geven aroysgegebn

00:14:41.270 --> 00:14:42.410
hob ikh aroysgenumen

00:14:42.410 --> 00:14:45.175
kh'hob gehat a bisl dolar. s'iz gelign mit mayn shver, t- g- n-

00:14:45.175 --> 00:14:45.975
er iz gelign

00:14:45.975 --> 00:14:47.935
un ikh hob UNK gebrengt groyse mashinen im

00:14:47.935 --> 00:14:49.295
un gebrengt nokh Shvedn

00:14:49.295 --> 00:14:50.762
un gemakht zikh a fabrik

00:14:50.762 --> 00:14:52.845
vos heyst UNK gezelshaft.

00:14:53.138 --> 00:14:55.342
kh'hob gekumen mit di zakhn, hob ikh gebrengt

00:14:55.467 --> 00:14:58.093
a por brilyantn, mitgevezn bahaltn

00:14:58.302 --> 00:14:59.730
hot a shved

00:15:00.225 --> 00:15:03.644
geganen, hot mir tsuge⟨UNK⟩ a tsveytn in LANDSKRONA a groyse fabrik

00:15:03.718 --> 00:15:07.728
in LANDSKRONA, un der hot gekoyft bay mir, un ikh bin gevorn mit im bakant

00:15:07.819 --> 00:15:12.015
un der hot gegat a groyse HURTOWNIA fun s- fun gesheftn, hot gegat

00:15:12.645 --> 00:15:15.139
dray, dray gesheftn

00:15:15.139 --> 00:15:17.529
un der krist hot zikh mit mir farhandlt

00:15:17.529 --> 00:15:19.729
un er hot mir tsugeshafn tsu farkoyfn

00:15:19.729 --> 00:15:23.699
un er hot mir gegebn zayne zun, un ikh hob gemakht a fabrik. kh'hob nisht getort makhn mayn nomen

00:15:23.699 --> 00:15:25.169
mit zey tsunezamen.

00:15:25.169 --> 00:15:28.400
un ikh, azoy hob ikh gemakht di fab- ershte fabrik fun bluzn

00:15:28.400 --> 00:15:32.080
un vos hot pasirt? farshteyst, der shved, eyner a shved geven a ganev.

00:15:32.080 --> 00:15:34.357
er hot gevolt mir tsunemen ales shoyn

00:15:34.357 --> 00:15:35.807
s'iz ganen zeyer gut

00:15:35.807 --> 00:15:37.357
iz er geganen, hot gezogt ikh ⟨az⟩

00:15:37.357 --> 00:15:39.960
me zol mir nisht gebn keyn erloybenish tsu blaybn in Shvedn.

00:15:40.320 --> 00:15:43.908
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu, hob ikh gekrign a k- an advokat

00:15:43.965 --> 00:15:45.531
iz er geven mayns a mentsh

00:15:45.531 --> 00:15:49.033
un er hot badarft oystsukoyfn mayn sh- yener hot gevolt oyszidlen

00:15:49.033 --> 00:15:51.013
hot gekrign, farshteystu

00:15:51.013 --> 00:15:52.703
a shved, a goy

00:15:52.703 --> 00:15:55.403
vos er iz geganen. er hot gemakht, farshteystu

00:15:55.403 --> 00:15:58.743
er hot gegebn ⟨borgt mir⟩ gelt, ikh veys nisht oyf vos kukedik

00:15:58.743 --> 00:16:00.668
demolt tsvontsik toyznt

00:16:00.668 --> 00:16:01.768
KRON

00:16:01.768 --> 00:16:03.468
iz azoy vi haynt gevezn

00:16:03.468 --> 00:16:05.568
fir hundert toyznt, rekhnt nisht.

00:16:05.568 --> 00:16:07.108
der goy hot mir geborgt

00:16:07.108 --> 00:16:10.568
geborgt di tsvontsik toyznt, un ikh hob ⟨banumen⟩ di fabrik

00:16:10.568 --> 00:16:14.149
un ikh hob gehat fertsik ayngeshtelte, un s'iz geloybt tsu got geganen mir gants gut.

00:16:14.273 --> 00:16:16.113
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu

00:16:16.113 --> 00:16:21.364
ikh bin an ander, mitn toyznt ⟨nayn hundert⟩ akht un ferts- ende ⟨an⟨ akht un fertsik fer- fuftsik

00:16:21.364 --> 00:16:22.414
nayn un fertsik

00:16:22.414 --> 00:16:24.664
kumt tsu forn fun di R.E.G.

00:16:24.664 --> 00:16:27.243
hot mikh oyfgezukht INZYNIER ⟨VAYDEMAN⟩

00:16:27.587 --> 00:16:29.246
ikh bin fun hoykh shpanung

00:16:29.246 --> 00:16:30.753
a spetsyalist

00:16:30.827 --> 00:16:31.816
vos heyst?

00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:34.314
m'hot gemakht a tsin fabrik. veyst vos tsin iz?

00:16:34.557 --> 00:16:36.039
⟨entsinderay⟩

00:16:36.039 --> 00:16:37.768
veyst ⟨vos⟩ taytsh ⟨entsindn⟩?

00:16:37.768 --> 00:16:41.067
me nemt arop di vayse blekh d- UNK di ⟨tsine⟩

00:16:41.067 --> 00:16:43.646
dos iz do tsvey in di velt vos hot gegat

00:16:43.804 --> 00:16:45.744
KAISER FRAZER in Amerike

00:16:45.744 --> 00:16:47.514
un GOLDSCHMIDT in Daytshland.

00:16:47.972 --> 00:16:49.640
dos iz zeyer vikhtik tsu hern,

00:16:49.640 --> 00:16:51.720
iz er gekumen tsu forn, hot men gehert ikh leb

00:16:51.720 --> 00:16:54.680
⟨me⟩ zol makhn UNK zayn fabrik, un ikh zol zayn der mayster.

00:16:54.891 --> 00:16:58.296
bin ikh geforn oyf di Shveyts, un gemakht UNK zayn fabrik

00:16:58.296 --> 00:16:59.666
iz geganen zeyer gut

00:16:59.666 --> 00:17:01.646
hot GOLDSCHMIDT gekoyft di fabrik.

00:17:01.646 --> 00:17:02.676
ikh muz avekgeyn.

00:17:02.676 --> 00:17:04.366
zenen mir geforn keyn Denmark

00:17:04.366 --> 00:17:06.356
un gemakht in Denmark di fabrik.

00:17:08.442 --> 00:17:09.313
JA

00:17:09.387 --> 00:17:12.807
in NEUNZEHN hundert akht un fertsik hob ikh khasene gegat

00:17:12.807 --> 00:17:16.917
UND mir SOLLTEN forn keyn keyn Amerike, keyn BOLIVIA

00:17:16.917 --> 00:17:20.404
UND es iz gevorn UNK zenen mir dort nisht geforn

00:17:20.404 --> 00:17:22.334
zenen mir geblibn in, in Shvedn

00:17:22.334 --> 00:17:23.794
un geloybt tsu got derfar

00:17:23.794 --> 00:17:29.029
un ikh hob a gants gute mishpokhe. der ershter zun hot zikh zeyer ⟨gut⟩, un der tsveyter zun

00:17:29.029 --> 00:17:30.289
iz er direktor fun

00:17:30.289 --> 00:17:32.899
fun farkoyfung funem gants, fun I.B.M.

00:17:32.899 --> 00:17:34.459
un di tokhter iz a ZAHNAR-

00:17:34.459 --> 00:17:36.351
der eydem hot patent byuro

00:17:36.351 --> 00:17:37.591
in ISRAEL

00:17:37.591 --> 00:17:40.191
farshteystu. m'hot fir, fir eyniklekh

00:17:40.191 --> 00:17:43.060
UND mayn zun hot dray, dray kinder

00:17:43.060 --> 00:17:44.950
UND

00:17:44.950 --> 00:17:46.771
azoy hob- WIR hobn UNK gants

00:17:46.771 --> 00:17:52.241
gants gut un, un al- ale hobn zikh zeyer gut. yetst hot men shoyn nokh an eynikl BEKOMMEN, u- un

00:17:52.241 --> 00:17:55.021
g- mayn z- tokhter hot BEK- -KOMMEN nokh an eynikl

00:17:55.021 --> 00:17:57.291
un mayn zun hot BEKOMMEN dos ershte eynikl

